{"tid":363673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【目無法紀】狂徒開槍狙擊　射爆路邊警車玻璃","createTime":"2017-08-17T20:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T04:54:38.000Z","uid":47714,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1849bea5b47c298d36798598ebd32ff86311cd1d","tid":363673,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:19:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170817/57091790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170817%2F57091790&d=OdrFYa418RfgzDrCgWZmgbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8e8fa4e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170817%2F57091790&h=55744572\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170817/57091790</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502945657_6ccd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502945657_6ccd.jpg&h=bba51c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上11時39分，一名女警駕駛警車，駛至北角渣華道近電廠街，並停靠路邊，其間聽到「呯」一聲響聲，發現警車右邊車門的玻璃應聲爆裂，並留下一個彈孔以及一顆鋼珠，於是通知上峰。多名同袍接報到場經調查，初步懷疑有人以氣槍射擊，將案列作刑事毀壞，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，至中午12時許，警方疑鎖定目標人物曾現身附近大廈，遂派出大批機動部隊警員，登上電器道一大廈蒐證。"},{"pid":"38c821d4eaf3c1159bd971902f48fdf3829d3e20","tid":363673,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:20:16.000Z","msg":"屌，彈石仔當開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134d83c8347c52264c6f2117a4fd41ae22b0917e","tid":363673,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:28:38.000Z","msg":"邊個巴打做既<br />\n出黎認左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6bb8065af5090933de6c2a1c74ebbdec950f72","tid":363673,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:50:5